name: Air-plane Parking 3D Sim-ulator
description: Plane Parking 3D is a 3D Airplane Parking Simulator game. You are the pilot of the plane and must park your plane in the correct bay within the airport, steer and drive your plane carefully around the airport and park up safely. Make sure you don't crash the plane into any obstacles or cones or you'll fail the level! Guide your plane into the green marked bay and park up to complete the level.
